reviews.text: A desert place that focuses on few delights (thick 4cm pancakes, shaved ice) and offers decent coffee and teas.  A small place with limited and tight seating.  Sofa seating along the wall is very upright with no cushioning, designed for space optimisation and not comfort.  Ingredients for its desert originate from Japan.  Worth a try.
